OL,6,FBetty recalls: "Her mother said to
OL,7,Fher, 'Don't touch anything, go and
OL,8,Fcall dad, he is digging the potatoes
OL,9,Fdown', so we went and she saw a little
OL,10,Fthing shining in the field.
OL,12,F"She went under the bobwire and it
OL,13,Fturns out it was a live mine and she
OL,14,Fwas blown up.
OL,16,F"I was sheltered by the hedge but she
OL,17,Fwas a bit of a dare-devil and didn't
OL,18,Flisten."
